# Template for the iroh services API secret. Copy to `iroh-services.env`
# and fill in. The real file is .gitignored. Do NOT commit a populated copy.
#
# Obtain a key at https://services.iroh.computer/ — used by the
# OpenBurnBarIroh xcframework + scripts/build-iroh-xcframework.sh to talk to
# iroh's hosted discovery / relay-management endpoints when applicable.
#
# This secret is ONLY used by the Mac host build / CI pipeline. iOS never
# embeds it and never sees it at runtime — Mac uses the iroh services API
# to publish relay-map updates and announce node availability if needed.

IROH_SERVICES_API_SECRET=
